These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, musical, thriller
House: futuristic, cottage, ranch-style, cape-cod
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the cottage house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the cape-cod house is between the cottage house and the ranch-style house##2
6. the person watching thriller movies is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | musical | disaster |
| House     | futuristic     | ranch-style | cape-cod  | cottage      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, cat, dog
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Pet     | hedgehog    | cat | guinea-pig | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, snowmobile, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| Transport           | trike | scooter | snowmobile | skateboard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
House: art-deco, craftsman, futuristic, palace
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the palace house is between the art-deco house and the egyptian##2
3. the palace house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the art-deco house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| House         | craftsman | art-deco | palace | futuristic  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
House: victorian, art-deco, tower, cottage
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, singing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the tower house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the art-deco house is on the right of the victorian house##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| House   | victorian    | art-deco   | tower | cottage    |
| Hobby      | hiking | drawing | singing       | woodworking |

