.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, epic, documentary, spy
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, train, tram
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the tram and the person watching documentary movies##2
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person watching time-travel movies##2
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Movie-Genre    | time-travel | documentary | spy | epic |
| Transport   | roller | boat  | train    | tram  |

