.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, indian, thai
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, august, july, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the egyptian##1
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the indian is between the french and the thai##2
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in july and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai | indian | french     |
| Birthday     | january | february  | august   | july |

