.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, montecristo, pall-mall, dunhill
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, scientific, superhero
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar         | dunhill | pall-mall | prince | montecristo   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific | horror      | superhero |

