.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
House: futuristic, victorian, farmhouse, tower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, skiing, tennis, volleyball
1. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the tower house##1
4. the futuristic house is on the left of the victorian house##1
5. the futuristic house is on the far left or far right##3
6. the victorian house is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| House     | futuristic | victorian   | farmhouse      | tower      |
| Sport   | skiing     | tennis | basketball | volleyball |

