.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, basketball, volleyball, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, tram
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | cricket | volleyball | water-polo    | basketball      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

