5. the fan of gospel is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | house     | indie  | rock | gospel |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | turtle | hamster     | rat    |

