.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, coral, lavender, aquamarine
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the librarian##3
2. the librarian is on the right of the manager##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who likes lavender is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Color   | coral  | lilac | aquamarine  | lavender      |
| Job    | musician | bartender | manager | librarian |

