.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, dancing, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, coach, librarian, security-guard
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
2. the coach is on the left of the librarian##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the security-guard##1
4. the coach is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the librarian is on the left or right of the coach##3
6. the librarian is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the coach is on the left or right of the architect##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | rock-climbing | dancing | card-games |
| Job   | security-guard     | architect       | coach   | librarian      |

