.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta, milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, february, may, august
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola    | milk  | fanta |
| Birthday   | november       | february | may | august  |

