.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, balloon-flower, sunflower, bellflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, security-guard
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
2. the security-guard is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the doctor is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the entrepreneur is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Flower   | bellflower        | poppy       | sunflower   | balloon-flower |
| Job    | security-guard | entrepreneur | doctor | coach  |

