.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, soy-milk
City: liverpool, prague, hannover, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta     | cola     | milk          | soy-milk |
| City      | liverpool | prague | edinburgh | hannover  |

 